051a80","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"ただ、すべきはエンドでのフィルタリングであって(IoT機器についてはまあルータでするしかないか)、IPv6使わないというのは、今だと前時代的で、OSのいろいろな機能が利用できなくなる面があるのですすめにくいというか、すすめる人の技術知識が気になるところ","ts":"1590968348.148700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"dDq"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"450e49b1-3c9b-44d6-8f76-08d56d5146a9","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"だめじゃないし、それも選択肢だろうけど","ts":"1590968365.149100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"3Cc"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"cf81e109-5321-41a5-911a-d93d7743f9b1","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"安全策は大事だし、そこは注意は継続してしなきゃいけないけど、IP reachableになることは、権利の復権の面あるんだけどなあ(NATのポート都合でゲーム他でトラブルとかあるわけで...)","ts":"1590968584.151400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"EJWk9"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"C2531449-F7D1-4C17-A2F9-1D1345013E7B","type":"message","user":"UDDCM376D","text":"IPv6全然わからないけど外からアクセスできるのは普通なんですね","ts":"1590969143.152700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"iyKL"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"ce632acf-5076-4d00-939f-8354894b483a","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"普通かまた微妙だけど、相互通信できることの重要性ってやっぱあるし","ts":"1590969167.153600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"ZXW"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"a00e8689-7af4-41ba-8158-8f31570e58c4","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"ただまあ、今回の記事のはIPv6をサービス的にOnしてないのに....はあるので、そこは気持ちわかるんだけど","ts":"1590969188.154100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type"