4-847b-3d43c9836e8c","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"PCはあんま繋がってるのみたことないかも?","ts":"1590970505.161800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"8oM"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"942889b6-fa07-4f7c-8871-44b3bac06e0d","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"あ、僕の自宅PC、つながってらw","ts":"1590970529.162500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"9vIn"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"8d924206-e189-4ee9-9552-d667955de203","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"そしてOSの機能として、わりと必要になったIPv6、ただリンクローカルと(届くときに)to Internetで繋がればいいし、逆にルータごしの接続ならSMBとかがくることも(基本は)ないので、そこまで神経質にしなきゃかな?という気もしている...まあ、無闇に開く必要がない、もわかる","ts":"1590970589.163700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"ZL5y"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"6C587DB5-7172-4F0B-A448-E6C3EDB42E08","type":"message","user":"UDDCM376D","text":"あー","ts":"1590970991.164000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"PY/"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"1F694CFD-E455-4C28-A14E-6E470BDC17EE","type":"message","user":"UDDCM376D","text":"ルーターまでがIPv6のパターンか","ts":"1590971004.164500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"AZL"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"E4B15D53-53A6-4718-9EEA-1EAA05A66E83","type":"message","user":"UDDCM376D","text":"あれ、ルーターってNAPTの機能でIP変換してるんでしたっけ？","ts":"1590971074.165500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"M+pS"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"89e4e46a-0cdc-4c01-adb0-e227604aca8d","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"プロバイダとの間でIPv6で繋がってるパターン、と言い換えたほうが良いかしらね。IPv6で繋がるのは結構珍しかったと思いますよ、NUROがでてきたときは。","ts":"1590971139.166500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"O6142"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"c5376532-5fcf-4be9-813b-4f2e6099b903","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"フレッツも内部はIPv6で、IPoEが有効になる契約すると、そのアドレスがふってくるのが、VNEの割り当てからになる、的な","ts":"1590971195.167200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"KPB91"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"A7E193CA-8D93-4B29-A4F3-0DE77613C46F","type":"message","user":"UDDCM376D","text":"ふむふむ","ts":"1590971225.168000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"zqSm6"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"d53320ed-48b7-42fb-a859-4594a742df84","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"そしてIPv6はNAPTしないのが基本です、アドレス空間広いので、普通に割り当てる、これでIP reachableになりえる","ts":"1590971226.168100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"b8j"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"df2487d4-965c-4be3-8ca6-22ab575731f7","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"ただ、そのまんまブリッジもこまるので、DHCPv6/RD proxy的にちゃんとするのが最近のルータ","ts":"1590971263.168700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"KcTlX"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"3806d95c-e0b5-4da5-b745-0caab11b97aa","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"それでも通信疎通はちゃんと保たれるし、それはかわらないけど","ts":"1590971291.169200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Qg="}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V